Our troops can take control of an enemy or neutral system from orbit by performing a planetary assault.  To launch an assault, right-click on the ship or fleet that is orbiting the target system and select 'Planetary Assault' from the pop-up menu. Note that a ship or fleet must contain troops in order to perform an assault and a system with two or more shields cannot be assaulted.  We must deploy Sabotage missions to destroy shields before our troops can be sent in.